co.poynt.os.contentproviders.search

Class SearchSuggestionContract

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.poynt.os.contentproviders.search.SearchSuggestionContract

  • public final class SearchSuggestionContract
extends java.lang.Object
    The Search Suggestion Content Provider is a virtual content provider used by the SearchManager to provide suggestions for user search. This provider should never be used like a normal provider. Created by vchau on 9/16/14.
